UnicodeDecodeError: 'ascii' codec can't decode byte 0xe4 in position 11: ordinal not in range(128)
```

### Setup
Build minion from develop.

### Steps to Reproduce Issue
Installed minion.
Started minion

### My guess 
Byte 0xe4 is at position 11 of "Mitteleurop√§ische Zeit" (Central European Time) represented as "Mitteleurop\xe4ische Zeit", which is my time zone.  [Guessed after](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/33295733/utf8-codec-cant-decode-byte-0xe4-invalid-continuation-byte-in-timezone)

How do I call `datetime.datetime.now(dateutil.tz.tzlocal()).tzname()`?


